{"title": "Why the US should welcome FDI from China", "tags": "opinion", "timestamp": "2024-08-27", "content": "A self-confessed \u201cheretical prophecy\u201d by the analyst Marko Papic landed in my e-mail inbox recently. Mr Papic is chief strategist at BCA Research, which produces analyses that are widely read by the investment community.\nIts title: Trump Will Make A Deal With China. Its bottom line: Threats of US tariffs on China will ultimately induce China to start producing electric vehicles (EVs) and, maybe, several other products as well in the United States, using American workers and developing US supply chains."}